          "quote": "Do not add comments that describe changes, progress, or historical modifications. Avoid comments like \"new function,\" \"added test,\" \"now we changed this,\" or \"previously used X, now using Y.\" Comments should only describe the current state and purpose of the code, not its history or evolution.",
